1.Ask the user for the numbers to perform calculation with using printf.
2. ask the user for the operator using prinf.                        
3. store the various user inputs using scanf.                       
4. check if user input meet with certain conditions using if statement:    
   if user inputs +, sum a and b together and print out.
   if user inputs -, subtract a and b together and print out.
   if user inputs *, mul a and b together and print out.
   if user inputs /, divide a and b together and print out.
